Steps to setup autorun virus using usb.

1. Copy and paste  'autorun.inf', 'inject.bat', 'virus.bat' into the root directory of your usb drive.

2. eject the usb drive.

3. USB drive is ready with the autoruning virus script.
[You dont need to format your usb drive. Usb drive data will be safe and secure.]

warning!

After pluging in the usb to any windows system the system will get infected with the virus. 
System cannot be disinfected manually.
Run the 'disinfect.bat' to remove the virus. 
